Come celebrate the end of classes with us this Wednesday at SwampSec <http://swampsec.org/>! If you don’t know what SwampSec is, it’s a gathering of infosec professionals that (mostly) takes place on the last Wednesday (7-9pm) of the month downtown at Stubbies & Steins <http://stubbiesandsteins.com/>. I even hear there will be free appetizers there! :)
